segmentosSRT.text: That's a big bowl, Youqing.

segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_10

segmentosSRT.text: All right. You go on ahead.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_10

segmentosSRT.text: Fengxia, you're back!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_10

segmentosSRT.text: Fengxia, you're going to be a mother.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_10

segmentosSRT.text: have a photo taken every year.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_10

segmentosSRT.text: Dad, I saw Chunsheng yesterday.

segmentosSRT.text:
We'll visit you after
she's out of the hospital.

segmentosSRT.text:

We've overthrown them.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_10

segmentosSRT.text: Relax. Your wife's fine. We can handle this.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_10

segmentosSRT.text: The working class is really something!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_10

segmentosSRT.text: It's a boy, 7.9 pounds.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_10

segmentosSRT.text: It doesn't matter. We're not done yet.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_10

segmentosSRT.text: Grandpa! It's crooked again.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_10

segmentosSRT.text: Granny, your medicine.

segmentosSRT.text: Back already?
